  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The objective of this study will be to prospectively evaluate the response of a continuous
      infusion of recombinant human antithrombin concentrate (rhAT) (ATRYN®) to achieve and
      maintain the AT activity within a specified range in adult patients that require
      extracorporeal membrane oxygenation (ECMO) following cardiopulmonary bypass (CPB) and
      cardiac surgery.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
